{"tid":2455320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻黃絲狗公係咁騷擾我女朋友點做好？","createTime":"2021-03-21T04:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T06:41:22.000Z","uid":247211,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3523d9975cffa859642af79555e830bdffc65e","tid":2455320,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqbQeXD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqbQeXD.png&h=6a8a7e11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uGgUXE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uGgUXE.png&h=40a6778a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行銷售主任Kenny Yip係下面呢個17萬fol既所謂文宣acc @memenewsharing 既管理員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMMTHZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMMTHZ3.jpg&h=953f57bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYuY8gM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYuY8gM.png&h=f94a03d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以為扮轉手改名就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omWs1Bp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomWs1Bp.png&h=4f93e95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前傳1：<br />\n<br />\n[有圖,警世]絲打小心呢個文宣ig<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958589</a><br />\n<br />\n前傳2：<br />\n<br />\n[多圖］遇到黃絲狗公割唔割？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2448861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2448861</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罪名1：20年4月已經有人開post話佢騷擾女仔，詳情可以參閱《前傳1》，當時Kenny Yip即時粒水扮死狗道歉同承諾唔會再用文宣acc溝女，件事就暫告一段落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLWTJhH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLWTJhH.jpg&h=0d1a8afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罪名2：控制言論仲要惡過共產黨，呢一年半載凡係有人留言質疑佢轉發既內容偏頗，佢就會立即blk無赦，依家直頭唔比人留言驚唔知咩事既人知道佢D狗公柒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmv9gGy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbmv9gGy.png&h=aec8e793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名3：一見女就狗衝，聲稱以後唔會再用呢個account撩女仔，但今日被多名女手足共同踢爆原來一直仲有繼續做狗公騷擾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ReUxYXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReUxYXs.png&h=b3f79c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWOriXt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWOriXt.png&h=4f26e290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pdbu39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pdbu39.png&h=1abce793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BznLzvP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBznLzvP.png&h=229afdce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZVtxhv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZVtxhv.png&h=204aa3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCwXqCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCwXqCw.png&h=bc2009e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名4：Kenny Yip滿口大話毫無誠信，係《前傳2》現真身否認經過《前傳1》後再有用此acc撩女仔，上面多張圖既日期可以佐證，同時多次宣稱會摺埋個page，唔再block人，結果又一次出爾反爾，支那人基因盡現<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EugAck5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEugAck5.png&h=28255476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xb107Ur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxb107Ur.png&h=64c34442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fsgwu7N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsgwu7N.png&h=7b92e124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rw4P7O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rw4P7O.png&h=0fca7b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xy9aLF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy9aLF8.png&h=66ec8f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ypqzzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ypqzzu.png&h=244a859a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名5：原來做文宣係食人血饅頭，為左準備第時去英國可以以黎做代購<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NhLzDB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NhLzDB.png&h=de51b2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罪名6：經常未經其他創作者同意偷圖偷post偷文，詳情可以參閱《前傳2》，屌你老母偷埋我篇文你食撚屎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F95X9Y3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF95X9Y3.png&h=1e169072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係有呢d毒瘤，文宣圈變撚左狗公圈<br />\n你仲follow，你就係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSJZD8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSJZD8P.png&h=acb3c003&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fe0bc66e464bba5b0e53c74b53dbd78afc4f2f9","tid":2455320,"uid":76272,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:46:50.000Z","msg":"私怨撚"},{"pid":"46da5a24b7cc69e643826b411566640328679957","tid":2455320,"uid":247211,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2fe0bc66e464bba5b0e53c74b53dbd78afc4f2f9","tid":2455320,"uid":76272,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-